module REQ_INV_DASH_01

/*
 * Alloy 6 ? Structural & Behavioral Model for Formal Verification
 * Requirement : REQ-INV-DASH-01
 * Title       : Inventory Dashboard Display
 * Type        : Functional
 * Priority    : High
